# Routing Sync Rule

- Source of truth for route map is `@docs/ROUTES.md`.
- Frontend routes are implemented in `@src/client/AppRouter.tsx`.
- API routes are implemented in `@src/server.ts`.

## When changing routes

- Update route tables in `docs/ROUTES.md` (path, method/access, description).
- Update navigation flow section if user journey changed.
- Remove stale endpoints from docs when code is removed.

## Verification

- Added route exists in code and docs with identical path.
- Renamed route is updated in all three places: client/server/docs.
